nodes.text: Kara was a Force-sensitive medic also training in the ways of the Jedi. She served on board the New Republic picket ship which discovered the only remaining Outrider-class cruiser belonging to the Order of the Silver Jedi. She accompanied Captain Korsu and his group when they boarded the cruiser and informed the captain that she felt darkness aboard. Immediately after she said this, the Force Vampire barreled through the group, grabbed onto her and drained her of her life.
